children.subject: random comment on 61a piazza says there will be an announcement today
I heard that 16A or 16B can be used to declare in lieu of 70

history.content: We'll meet today. Updates will appear in @11615

Can we get an update/estimate on where does the department stand vis a vis the new policy of PNP and how does it affect declaration?

I understand that these things take time and the concerned people must be doing everything within their power to get it done.

But this is just an appeal to maybe make it a bit faster or give us an estimate as it has becoming increasingly difficult to be upto with the content and study for the midterm while my country is under a lockdown and struggling for essential goods. If we can get an update, then I can devote my time on prioritizing my health and be rest assured about the declaration. An estimate of when the decision would be out would also help!

Thank you.
